snippet.title: Ammossum announcement trailer [ENG]
snippet.description:
🌵 After a year of passionate development, we're thrilled to share some great news – Ammossum now has its own Steam page!

You can add the game to your wishlist right now:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2659600/Ammossum/

Stay tuned for updates on the demo release and follow our development journey!

#indiegame #trailer #newgame #gaming #roguelike
